<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Craftopedia</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background: #fff5f7;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    h1 {
      text-align: center;
      color: #d6336c;
    }
    .step {
      background: white;
      margin: 20px auto;
      max-width: 800px;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .step img {
      width: 200px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      margin-right: 20px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>


<h1>Craftopedia – Paper Flower</h1>


<div class="step">
  <img src="images/step1.jpg">
  <p>Step 1: Take colored paper and fold it neatly.</p>
</div>


<div class="step">
  <img src="images/step2.jpg">
  <p>Step 2: Draw a flower pattern on the paper.</p>
</div>


<div class="step">
  <img src="images/step3.jpg">
  <p>Step 3: Cut along the drawn outline.</p>
</div>


<div class="step">
  <img src="images/step4.jpg">
  <p>Step 4: Open the paper and shape the petals.</p>
</div>


<div class="step">
  <img src="images/step5.jpg">
  <p>Step 5: Stick layers together using glue.</p>
</div>


</body>
</html>